th.setnonce-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="methodname">{@link OAuth::setToken()} - 设置令牌和 secret</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="methodname">{@link OAuth::setAuthType()} - 设置授权类型</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="methodname">{@link OAuth::setVersion()} - 设置 OAuth 版本</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.oauth.php">OAuth</a></div></div>
